description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, a government employee in Pennsylvania claimed she was the victim of a racist incident involving a noose. Surprising no one, it turns out it was a hoax — like literally every other racist noose incident this century. Also, we’ll discuss a shocking story in Colorado of a teacher who essentially claimed custody over one of her gender-confused students, even as her actual parents desperately try to get the child back. Plus, the war on Teslas continues, as the Tesla vandals get dumber by the day.
